				<h4>Shipping Policy:</h4>
				<p> Standard shipping is free for ALL orders above Rs.99/- and for orders less than Rs.99/- standard shipping charges of Rs 100/- will apply.</p>
				<p> Orders shipped via Shiprocket courier will take 2-3 Days, Orders shipped via an economy courier may take up to 5-8 days depending on your location. </p>
