				<p>You can also track the shipping status of your order on our website, by visiting the <b>Track your Order section.</b></p>
				<p>Please note Shop99 is closed on Sunday and major holidays. Orders received on Saturday after 12 pm and Sunday will begin processing the following Monday.</p>
				<p>If you do not receive your tracking email please contact: <b>support@shop99.co.in</b></p>

